{
  "texts": [
    "The supernatants were used for protein purification using the following procedures.",
    "Talon resins (cat. no.",
    "635653, Takara Bio) were washed twice with a binding buffer (50 mM NaH 2 PO 4, 300 mM NaCl, 10 mM imidazole, pH 7.4) and then suspended in the same volume of binding buffer as the resin bed amount.",
    "Talon resin (50 μl) was loaded into Pierce microspin columns (cat. no.",
    "89879, ThermoFisher)."
  ]
}